long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Dubo is your AI assistant for writing faster, cheaper, and smarter SQL. This Chrome extension integrates Dubo seamlessly into Snowflake, allowing you to tab-complete individual lines of a query or describe the desired query through a comment, and have the AI write the whole thing for you.

Learn more about Dubo at https://dubo.gg/.

Developed by Mercator Technologies.

By installing this extension, you agree to the Mercator Terms of Service at https://mercator.tech/terms and Privacy Policy at https://mercator.tech/privacy.
